            <title>[DATAREST-311] executeSearchCompact - Mismatch argument name and path variable name</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/DATAREST-311</link>
                <project id="10901" key="DATAREST">Spring Data REST</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In the RepositorySearchController class, the method executeSearchCompact does not take the right argument.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This case happens when the Accept values in the Request Header contains application/*+json&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If you use the browser, no issue can be detected.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
